<quantity box="[581,636,1979,2006]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" pageId="48" pageNumber="49" unit="km" value="8.0">8 km</quantity>
<superScript attach="left" box="[636,644,1979,1993]" fontSize="6" pageId="48" pageNumber="49">2</superScript>
and two localities (or subpopulations).The species is widely distributed in all South America.
</paragraph>
